  taskTitle: Draft This
  taskDescription: 'What is the best investment strategy '
  messageToType: "The best long-term investment strategy for most people is consistent
    investing in low-cost, diversified index funds while avoiding emotional decision-making.
    Regularly contributing (like monthly) to broad market ETFs such as an S&P 500
    or total market fund allows you to benefit from compound growth over time. Keep
    fees low, reinvest dividends, and hold through market downturns instead of trying
    to time the market. The real edge isn\u2019t picking stocks \u2014 it\u2019s
    staying disciplined for 10\u201320+ years."
